name: Adobi's Real Flexible Mix [aah!]
description:
A merge series focusing on realism with room for creativity to pull away from stock photo vibes.

~ Adobi : I wanted a general model to get more experimental with my generations while still aiming for a realistic feel.

Update : Opensource alternative available as Adobi's Real Open Mix

Focuses

  • Portraits, Landscapes

  • Realism, Paintings, Illustrations, CG, Concept Art

Settings

Sampling : Euler A (25), Heun, DDIM (60)
CFG Scale : 5.5 - 8.5
Hires. fix : R-ESRGAN 4x+, 25 Hires steps and Denoising strength 0.4

Suggested Prompts

~ Mix'N'Match, don't need to use all of them

Realism : Cinematic film still, analog style, RAW photo, hyper real photo, ultrarealistic uhd faces, 8k uhd, dslr, soft lighting, high quality, film grain, Fujifilm XT3, photographed on a Canon EOS R5, 50mm lens, F/2.8, HDR, hyper-realistic, colorgraded, volumetric lighting, volumetric fog, moist, shallow depth of field, reflections

Suggested Negatives

General : blurry, logo, watermark, signature, cropped, out of frame, worst quality, low quality, jpeg artifacts, poorly lit, overexposed, underexposed, glitch, error, out of focus

Realism / General : (semi-realistic, cgi, 3d, render, sketch, cartoon, drawing, digital art, anime, manga:1.3), amateur

Realism / Portrait : (poorly drawn hands, poorly drawn face:1.2), deformed iris, deformed pupils, morbid, duplicate, mutilated, extra fingers, mutated hands, poorly drawn eyes, mutation, deformed, dehydrated, bad anatomy, bad proportions, extra limbs, cloned face, disfigured, gross proportions, malformed limbs, missing arms, missing legs, extra arms, extra legs, fused fingers, too many fingers, long neck

SFW : nsfw, naked, exposed breasts, nude, nudity, erotic

~ will be adding more categories for suggestions soon...

Known Keywords :

analog style, modelshoot style, alluring blue eyes, cyborgdiffusion, erotic, nsfw, nudity, elden ring style, postapocalypse, knollingcase, swpunk, synthwave, dreamlikeart, mdjrny-v4 style, nousr robot, tiktok, instagram

~ comment if you pick up anything particularly interesting

Recommended Additions :

  • Textual Inversions :

    • bad_prompt, bad-artist, EasyNegative, bad_quality, bad-hands-5, bad-image-v2-39000, NG_DeepNegative_V1_32T

  • Hypernets :

    • sxzBloom_sxzBloom, LuisapPhotoclarity_v1, LuisapProPortrait_v1

  • LORAs :

    • cher70s_v10, lomodiffusionLora300_lomodiffusionLora300, analogdiffusion_Lora300, LuisapNijijourneyLORAV2_v2, loraBasedOnPaintingsBy_zdzislawBeksinski, dalcefopainting_Lora300, photovintageLORA64_photovintagev15, s1dlxbrewLora302_s1dlxbrewLora302, skinTextureDreamlike_LoRA300

Reffed Models in version info.

credit to phantasion for some of the example pics.
